lyrics:
[Verse]
Dr. Ghomi comes in, with gloves on his hands
A tooth so loose, it's time to take a stand
Patient feeling nervous, in the dental chair
The room fills with tension, a touch of despair

[Chorus]
Extracting with precision, gauze in his grip
Dr. Ghomi's expertise, never let it slip
Tooth pulled away, bid farewell to its reign
Gauze to the rescue, alleviating pain
